report.dependency-info.title

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>nl.cbs.cbsviewer</groupId>
  <artifactId>cbsviewer</artifactId>
  <version>1.1-SNAPSHOT</version>
  <type>war</type>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'nl.cbs.cbsviewer:cbsviewer:war:1.1-SNAPSHOT'

Apache Ant

<dependency org="nl.cbs.cbsviewer" name="cbsviewer" rev="1.1-SNAPSHOT">
  <artifact name="cbsviewer" type="war" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='nl.cbs.cbsviewer', module='cbsviewer', version='1.1-SNAPSHOT')
)

Grails

compile 'nl.cbs.cbsviewer:cbsviewer:1.1-SNAPSHOT'

Leiningen

[nl.cbs.cbsviewer/cbsviewer "1.1-SNAPSHOT"]

SBT

libraryDependencies += "nl.cbs.cbsviewer" %% "cbsviewer" % "1.1-SNAPSHOT"
